Description: ===================
        pytest-faulthandler
        ===================
        
        Plugin for pytest that automatically enables the
        `faulthandler <https://faulthandler.readthedocs.io/>`_ module during tests.
        
        Inspired by the
        `nose faulthandler <https://github.com/schlamar/nose-faulthandler>`_ plugin.
        
